    - SAUCE: (efi-lockdown) MODSIGN: Import certificates from UEFI Secure Boot
    - SAUCE: (efi-lockdown) MODSIGN: Support not importing certs from db
    - SAUCE: (efi-lockdown) MODSIGN: Don't try secure boot if EFI runtime is
      disabled
